A y/n flag that applies to covered bonds and provides information on their compliance with European Union Regulation (EU) No 575/2013 (Capital Requirements Regulation  CRR), article 129. If set to y, the flag indicates that the security is CRR compliant. If set to n the flag indicates that the security is non-compliant. If the flag is NULL, the EU Regulation is either not applicable (i.e. for non-covered bonds) or the compliance cannot be confirmed.
